        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Federal Law Enforcement Officer Service Weapon Purchase Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill directs the General Services Administration to establish a program under which a federal law enforcement officer may purchase a retired firearm from the agency that issued the firearm to the officer.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
